{"tid":1737811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一位忠師喺第四維度上觀察住香港，會心微笑","createTime":"2019-11-19T05:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T11:57:02.000Z","uid":154702,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"25093d229a206ed877dc1a8efb46e8dab7d38393","tid":1737811,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:09:50.000Z","msg":"如果人死之後可以擺脫三維空間<br />\n我諗佢一定係第四維度- 時間線上面會心微笑<br />\n估唔到自己1971 年接受訪問嘅時候<br />\n講嘅幾句說話(其實係電視劇對白, 詳見下)<br />\n影響香港2019年打後嘅命運<br />\nBe water, my friend. <br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/vBsbmDX95Idfq/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FvBsbmDX95Idfq%2Fgiphy.gif&h=e831d1fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 致手足<br />\n不受浪漫主義影響判斷<br />\n不受敵方牽著鼻子決定戰鬥方式<br />\n不忘死傷手足遺志<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LTnSEFsInp0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLTnSEFsInp0&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfHs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=dc816e3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LTnSEFsInp0</a>"},{"pid":"1620fc07b145a8f0b79b1840231fdf3be2f1b59b","tid":1737811,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:10:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n【行動】Twitter 戰線：世界各地政要火力全開！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入----------&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfHs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=341ac1f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"26c6a505a89831b80268bf8c2ee4865295934ae3","tid":1737811,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s